(212, 1, '2017-10-16 13:55:11', '2017-10-16 13:55:11', 'Too often risk management is seen as reactive, but nothing could be further from the truth. In this Risk Management training course you will learn to work through a proactive approach to risk threat and opportunity. You will address how to identify, quantify, control and respond to risk management in the context of the project life-cycle. Learn qualitative and quantitative techniques and tools for assessing the impact of risk. Through interactive exercises and case studies, participants will be able to apply risk management theories, concepts and principles to real-world situations.', 'Management of Risk', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '104-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-10-16 13:55:11', '2017-10-16 13:55:11', '', 104, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/10/16/104-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
